content:
Financial Services Cloud

Manage Standing Instructions Service Process (Unmanaged Package)

Your customers can use this service process to raise requests for adding or removing instructions for setting up recurring and timely payments from any of their investment accounts.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

Setup and Configuration of the Manage Standing Instructions Service Process
Use the Service Process Studio to enable the Manage Standing Instructions service process to give your agents an easy-to-follow process for capturing the customer requests.

Submit a Manage Standing Instructions Request
Your service agents can capture and submit a Manage Standing Instructions request by using the Manage Standing Instructions OmniScript.
title: Managing Standing Instructions in Financial Services Cloud
